You asked, and we are proud to deliver! 🫡 This online education platform will start with our highly requested 𝘼𝙨𝙨𝙞𝙨𝙩𝙖𝙣𝙩 𝙀𝙙𝙞𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣, with more education to follow.❤️‍🔥

Let’s chat 😜⬇️

First, let me know if you want the deets on this color application in the comments!

Second, this is absolutely ✨not✨ a realistic outcome for every client. Several factors play into this transformation, including integrity of the client’s hair, her hair history, budget, time, and her willingness to trim. She was told that her hair would be very fragile after such a major transformation and committed to a strict at home product and care regimen. We love a dedicated client. 😇

@morgan.tailored and I had so much fun tackling this today and making it our bishhhhhh💪🏼🙌🏽

AND OIL THOSE ENDS😤 I can’t remember the last time I washed my hair 🤭 that’s my real secret 🤫

6.11.23 𝕄𝕒𝕣𝕜 𝕪𝕠𝕦𝕣 𝕔𝕒𝕝𝕖𝕟𝕕𝕒𝕣𝕤!

Brandie, 🅣🅗🅔 🅞🅖, will be doing a 𝖇𝖑𝖔𝖓𝖉𝖎𝖓𝖌 overhaul on her model. She will show you how she takes a blonde from “just a blonde” to the “𝑰̲̅𝑻̲̅ 𝑮̲̅𝑰̲̅𝑹̲̅𝑳̲̅ 𝑩̲̅𝑳̲̅𝑶̲̅𝑵̲̅𝑫̲̅𝑬̲̅.” She leaves no hair untouched and refuses to settle for basic 𝖆𝖘𝖘 hair.

Megan, ᴛʜᴇ ɴᴇᴡʙɪᴇ, will be tackling a 𝖇𝖑𝖔𝖓𝖉𝖊-𝖙𝖔-𝖇𝖗𝖚𝖓𝖊𝖙𝖙𝖊 makeover. Taking a blonde canvas and turning it into an eye-catching bronde with the most 𝙞𝙣𝙩𝙚𝙣𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙖𝙡 foil placement. She believes nothing beats 𝖉𝖎𝖒𝖊𝖓𝖘𝖎𝖔𝖓𝖆𝖑 𝖈𝖔𝖑𝖔𝖗 and has perfected this fool proof technique.

There will be a light lunch served, complimentary swag bags, giveaways, and a 30 minute Q+A to end the class.

Huge shout out to @amberandsagehairco for hosting us! SPOTS ARE LIMITED. Don’t wait. Link in bio to purchase your ticket.
